  "title": "Nutrient Cascade Rewrite",
  "concept": "When a new input floods a system with nutrients, the first change triggers a second, the second triggers a third — each shift creates the condition for the next, rewriting the whole system through linked responses.",
  "interactiveId": "74d3424a-daab-46af-83e0-3750578124a9",
  "sourcePieceId": "b00d9a30-65e6-4c6e-9b96-da7d8d9dcbe9",
